## Store Highlights
The Gift Studio, founded in 2019 and headquartered in Mumbai, has established itself as a premium gifting destination in India. As part of the RPSG Group's Nature's Basket Limited, the company focuses on redefining the gifting landscape with exclusively curated hampers that move beyond generic presents to create memorable experiences.

